					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Rinaldo Walcott</h4>
												<p>Rinaldo Walcott is a Professor in the Women and Gender Studies Institute at the University of Toronto. His research is in the area of Black Diaspora Cultural Studies, gender and sexuality.</p>
